short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A tool for developers to create branches more quickly and efficiently.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hubbe Git Tooling is a cutting-edge extension designed specifically for developers. It streamlines the process of creating git branches, making it faster and more efficient. With just a few clicks, developers can set up new branches without the usual hassle. By installing Hubbe Git Tooling, users will enhance their workflow, save valuable time, and focus on what truly matters: coding. Experience a new level of git management and elevate your development process today!
